{"id": "art-1432", "label": "Art. 1432", "title": "Art. 1432", "slug": "art-1432", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_331391641\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2193\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_331391641\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 143<sup>2</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1030636192\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2192\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1030636192\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\nreprezint&#259; societatea în raport cu <span class=SpellE>ter&#355;ii</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> în <span class=SpellE>justi&#355;ie</span>. În\nlipsa unei <span class=SpellE>stipula&#355;ii</span> contrare în actul\nconstitutiv, consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\nreprezint&#259; societatea prin <span class=SpellE>pre&#351;edintele</span>\ns&#259;u.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1259629917\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2191\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1259629917\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Prin actul constitutiv, <span class=SpellE>pre&#351;edintele</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> unul sau mai <span class=SpellE>mul&#355;i</span>\nadministratori pot fi <span class=SpellE>împuternici&#355;i</span> s&#259;\nreprezinte societatea, <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionând</span> împreun&#259;\nsau separat. O astfel de clauz&#259; este opozabil&#259; <span class=SpellE>ter&#355;ilor</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1084321547\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2190\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1084321547\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Prin acordul lor unanim, administratorii care\nreprezint&#259; societatea doar <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionând</span>\nîmpreun&#259; pot împuternici pe unul dintre ei s&#259; încheie anumite <span\nclass=SpellE>opera&#355;iuni</span> sau tipuri de <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iuni</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_10778038\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2189\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_10778038\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)În cazul în care consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\ndeleag&#259; directorilor <span class=SpellE>atribu&#355;iile</span> de\nconducere a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> în conformitate cu\nart. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>143</span><span style='color:black'>,\nputerea de a reprezenta societatea <span class=SpellE>apar&#355;ine</span>\ndirectorului general. <span class=SpellE>Dispozi&#355;iile</span> alin. (2)\n-(4) se aplic&#259; directorilor în mod corespunz&#259;tor. Consiliul de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span> p&#259;streaz&#259; îns&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>atribu&#355;ia</span> de reprezentare a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nîn raporturile cu directorii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1418745053\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2188\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1418745053\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\nînregistreaz&#259; la registrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>\nnumele persoanelor împuternicite s&#259; reprezinte societatea, <span\nclass=SpellE>men&#355;ionând</span> dac&#259; ele <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ioneaz&#259;</span>\nîmpreun&#259; sau separat.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}